## 📌 Conclusion

This project demonstrates how SQL can be used to transform raw Airbnb data into actionable business insights. Through pricing analysis, occupancy estimation, host evaluation, neighbourhood comparison, and revenue estimation, the project showcases practical SQL techniques commonly used by data analysts to support business decision-making.
